{"tid":396210,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"文迪：去車路士？我寧願留隊！","createTime":"2017-09-11T13:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T15:47:01.000Z","uid":26959,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"681c68ef0e121ef2d09164a708b4608c483f0475","tid":396210,"uid":26959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:24:27.000Z","msg":"Manchester City summer signing Benjamin Mendy 'never wanted to join Chelsea', reveals Monaco vice president.<br />\n<br />\nMonaco vice president Vadim Vasilyev has revealed Benjamin Mendy never wanted a move to Chelsea.<br />\n<br />\nThe defender joined Manchester City this summer in a &pound;52million dea;, but before that he was also linked with a move to Stamford Bridge.<br />\n<br />\nHowever, Vasilyev has now revealed that Mendy was never going to force through a move to Chelsea as he was only interested in playing for Pep Guardiola.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;At first, I said, 'No, you're staying,'&quot; Vasilyev told L'Equipe.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;He replied: 'But Vadim, I really want to go to City and link up with Guardiola.'<br />\n<br />\n&quot;On numerous occasions he said to me: 'If it was Chelsea, I'd stay; but if it's a chance to work with Guardiola, I want to go.'<br />\n<br />\n&quot;He'd spoken so frankly with me. So, when City met the asking price and when he became the most expensive defender in the world, there were no more arguments to have with him.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n睇我地車路士唔起=.=?"},{"pid":"197dcc11285ceff62a7c977f835855987d3ccafb","tid":396210,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T16:15:27.000Z","msg":"樓主又陰啲陰啲反車"},{"pid":"2d3762ff54ae25b4d6c58603b7826648c7559ff2","tid":396210,"uid":54025,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T16:18:05.000Z","msg":"斷腳啦仆街，粉碎性個隻添啊撚樣文迪！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/PBARhBEIazpte/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm